steps for execution of largest digit in number
step 1 :Take the number  as user input n
step 2 :Take each digits of the number using while loop until n is not equal to 0
step 3 :take temporary variable as temp and l 
step 4 :each digit is stored in temp using n%10
step 5 :check if the temp is greater than l or not 
step 6 :if temp grater than l then  assign l with temp
         it will check for each digit
step 7 :if l is greater than all the digits in a number then print l is greater digit
         
 